        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Upcoming Events
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Join me for live sessions on vibe coding, AI-assisted development, and software engineering fundamentals. 
          Learn from real-world examples and get your questions answered in interactive workshops.
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Events Section -->
